questions.sparqlQuery:
PREFIX  rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX  prop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>

SELECT  ?string
WHERE
  { ?dog  rdfs:label    "Airedale Terrier"@en ;
          prop:country  ?string
  }

languageToQuestion.en: Which country does the Airedale Terrier come from?

questions.sparqlQuery:
PREFIX  res:  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX  onto: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>

SELECT  ?number
WHERE
  { res:IBM  onto:revenue  ?number }

languageToQuestion.de: Was ist das Einnahmen von IBM?
languageToQuestion.pt: o que é a receita do IBM?
languageToQuestion.en: What is the revenue of IBM?
languageToQuestion.it: Che cosa è il reddito di IBM?
languageToQuestion.fa: یچ  تسا  نیا  دمآرد  زا  ؟ما یب یآ
languageToQuestion.fr: Quelle est la revenu de IBM?
languageToQuestion.es: Qué es el ingresos de IBM?
languageToQuestion.nl: Wat is de omzet van IBM?
